# - Object Lock must be enabled at bucket creation time and cannot be changed afterward.
# - The object_lock_enabled_for_bucket parameter must be set to true.

# Step 2: Configure default retention
# - To set default retention, we need a default_retention configuration within object_lock_configuration.
# - The mode should be "COMPLIANCE" and period set to 30 days.

# Step 3: Ensure all required arguments are provided
# - bucket: Name of the bucket (example-bucket)
